
### Variables (Update this to localhost:5000 for local testing)
@baseUrl = https://travels-works.onrender.com/api

### 1. Health Check: Get All Destinations
# Tests if the database connection and "Explore" section data are working.
GET {{baseUrl}}/destinations
Accept: application/json

---

### 2. Fetch All Reviews
# This pulls the data used for your centered overall rating display.
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Accept: application/json

---

### 3. Submit a New Review
# Use this to test if your rating display updates in real-time.
# The 'stars' value (1-5) will affect your overall average rating.
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ajay",
  "role": "Verified Explorer",
  "stars": 5,
  "text": "Amazing service! The guides were very knowledgeable and the booking was easy.",
  "avatar": "https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=ajay"
}

---

### 4. Create a New Booking
# Tests the lead generation form logic.
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Traveler",
  "email": "traveler@example.com",
  "number": "9123456789",
  "location": "Tirupati Temple Visit"
}

---

### 5. Fetch All Bookings (Admin Check)
# Use this to verify that the bookings sent in step 4 were actually saved.
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Accept: application/json
